description:
 職責:
1) 負責接送公司及家庭成員
2) 負責中港車輛續牌、各項證件辦理及保險續保等事宜
3) 負責維持車輛日常清潔、維修保養安排及相關工作
4) 需外勤:協助處理銀行入數、遞送急件、其他行政工作及臨時委派的任務
5) 支援行政部日常運作暢順


要求:
-五年或以上任職公司或私人司機經驗;
-持有中港駕駛執照及有中港駕駛經驗;
-中五畢業, 最少5年公司/私人司機經驗;
-良好駕駛態度及記錄流利粵語、一般普通話、簡單英語溝通;
-持有效香港及內地駕駛執照、熟識中港車輛證件辦理、續牌、續保等辦理流程;
-熟識香港及廣東省行車路線及中港道路交通條例;
-可應需求在工作時間以外及假期加班工作;
-整潔有禮、守時、保密、誠實可靠、有責任心及不吸煙;
-懂得簡單使用電腦 (電郵);
-香港區工作

福利 
每週工作5天、銀行假期、年終雙糧、醫療保險、意外保險、有薪婚假、生日假、加班費、 膳食津貼等

申請須知 :求職者可致電 / Whatsapp 5291-7722與陳小姐聯絡。
有意申請者請按Apply Now

職位要求:

最少5年駕駛房車或七人車經驗，並曾任公司/ 私人司機 ;
良好駕駛記錄及態度，無不良嗜好 ;
誠實有禮、守時及責任感 ;
須持有效中港私家車駕駛執照，熟悉香港及國內道路和交通條例 ;
讀寫簡單中、英文; 略懂普通話 ;
有需要時願意超時工作

工作內容:

負責接載公司管理層、高級行政人員及指定人士 ;
確保公司車輛清潔、跟進維修保養、驗車及車輛續牌事宜 ;
執行其他臨時委派的任務 ;
按工作需要駕駛往來中港兩地 ;
出車地點: 中環

工作時間:

每週工作六天、須輪休、每天工作約10小時 ;
因應工作安排，偶爾需於假日工作或需超時工作

銀行福利:

銀行假期、醫療(含家屬)、牙醫津貼、表現花紅、其他銀行福利

按 APPLY NOW申請

Responsibilities:
- Coordinate daily operation of vehicle and jobs of drivers
- Take orders from customers, communicate with drivers
- Handling documents & computer/Apps operation


Requirements :
- Secondary 5;
- 2 Years Experience Required;
- Fluent Cantonese & Fair English ; 
- Experiences in transportation coordination & documents handling preferred;
- English & chinese typing, tsangjei or simplified tsangjei input method (30WPM);
- Computer operation especially good command of Excel ;
- Knowledge in route pref.


Employment Terms:
- $13,000 - $16,000 per month,
- with Double Pay, Bank Holiday, Good Attendance Bonus and Medical Insurance
- Alternative Saturday off after probation

Job Responsibilities


Provide security and driving services to the employer;
Handle any matters assigned by the employer.

Job Requirements


Have relevant experience in security services;
Have any professional security or close protection qualifications;
Holder of valid Security Personnel Permit;
Holder of driving license;
Strong sense of responsibility, honest and confidentiality.

We offer good career prospects to the right candidate. Interested parties please send detailed resume with availability, current and expected salary by clicking "Apply". 

(Applications will be treated in strict confidence. Personal data collected will be used for recruitment purpose only.)

時薪: HK$73.5

工作概要:

停車場巡查;
確認合適泊車証及安排適當泊車位置;
控制交通，令行人及車輛暢順;
交通設施/標記擺設;
登記停車場泊車記錄及解答客人查詢

工作時間:

星期三: 15:30 至 23:30 或
星期六: 10:00 至 19:00 或
星期日: 10:00 至 19:00

Responsibilities:


         Driving duties for Executive Directors and families;
         Follow up on car maintenance and ensure safety and cleanliness of the car;
         Follow up on HK car licenses application / renewal;
         Working hours: 7 am to 7 pm, 6 days a week

Requirements:



At least 5-8 years driving experience in serving directors / guests
Familiar with traffic conditions, regulations and roads in HK
Willing to work overtime and on holidays;
Strong sense of road safety and positive driving records;
Responsible, punctual, polite and tidy

Benefits:

Attractive salary package with OT allowance, meal allowance, mobile allowance
Medical Insurance, Dental Insurance, Life Insurance
Performance bonus

If you have interest for this position, you can contact us by 31966253 for more company details.
